Achievements.Name: First Finish
Achievements.Description: Awarded for finishing your first race.

Achievements.Name: Globe Trotter
Achievements.Description: Awarded for finishing a race in all the stadiums in career mode.

Achievements.Name: Season 2 Promotion
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you are promoted from Season 1 to Season 2.

Achievements.Name: Season 3 Promotion
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you are promoted from Season 2 to Season 3.

Achievements.Name: Backstroke Winner
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning a Backstroke race in career mode.

Achievements.Name: Breaststroke Winner
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning a Breaststroke race in career mode.

Achievements.Name: Butterfly Winner
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning a Butterfly race in career mode.

Achievements.Name: Front Crawl Winner
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning a Front Crawl race in career mode.

Achievements.Name: Hair Trigger
Achievements.Description: Awarded for Jumping the Gun in a career race.

Achievements.Name: Optimum Dive
Achievements.Description: Awarded for achieving an Optimum Dive in any race.

Achievements.Name: Optimum Turn
Achievements.Description: Awarded for achieving an Optimum Turn in any race.

Achievements.Name: Optimum Finish
Achievements.Description: Awarded by achieving a Good Reach in any race.

Achievements.Name: Pool Legend
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you complete Season 3 in Career Mode.

Achievements.Name: Annual Games Debut
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you play for the first time in the Annual Games.

Achievements.Name: Hyped Up
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you max out the pre-race crowd excitement meter.
